author: kkolinko
msg: Recommend to copy the servlet into one's own web application instead of uncommenting it globally.
The default value for cgiPathPrefix is null. The "WEB-INF/cgi" value is the recommended one and used in conf/web.xml example.

author: desruisseaux
msg: Merge from the JDK6 branch only selected changes:
TopicCategory, PixelOrientation and Obligation CodeList became Enum on GeoAPI-SNAPSHOT
for ISO 19115 compliance, but we keep them in their old form on trunk for compatibility.
